tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE influencer_outreach (
    influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email_address VARCHAR(255),
    outreach_date DATE,
    response_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE influencers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    followers_count INT,
    engagement_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE outreach_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    email_date TIMESTAMP,
    email_subject VARCHAR(255),
    response_rate FLOAT,
    response_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE EmailCommunications (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    subject VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    body TEXT NOT NULL,
    sent_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES Influencers(id)
);

CREATE TABLE ResponseRates (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    communication_id INT,
    response_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    response_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (communication_id) REFERENCES EmailCommunications(id)
);

CREATE TABLE EmailCommunications (
  email_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_id INT,
  subject VARCHAR(255),
  body TEXT,
  sent_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE influencer_outreach (
  influencer_id UUID,
  email_address VARCHAR(255),
  communication_date DATE,
  response_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
  PRIMARY KEY (influencer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE outreach_content (
  content_id UUID,
  influencer_id UUID,
  content_title VARCHAR(255),
  content_type VARCHAR(50),
  PRIMARY KEY (content_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencer_outreach(influencer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE emails (
  email_id UUID,
  influencer_id UUID,
  email_subject VARCHAR(255),
  email_body TEXT,
  email_date TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (email_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencer_outreach(influencer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE response_rates (
  influencer_id UUID,
  response_id UUID,
  response_date DATE,
  response_rating DECIMAL(3,1),
  PRIMARY KEY (response_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencer_outreach(influencer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE outreach_performance (
  influencer_id UUID,
  outreach_date DATE,
  outreach_success BOOLEAN,
  outreach_notes TEXT,
  PRIMARY KEY (influencer_id, outreach_date),
  FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencer_outreach(influencer_id)
);
